Bank of Spain Seeks Funds To Invest in Cajas, Vabguardia Reports

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-05-30T06:28:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/bank-of-spain-seeks-funds-to-invest-in-cajas-vabguardia-reports.html
The Bank of  Spain  is seeking funds
specialized in banks to invest in savings banks, La Vanguardia
reported.  The process of seeking investors is most advanced in the
case of  Caja de Ahorros del Mediterraneo (CAM)  and Novacaixagalicia,
the newspaper said, citing people close to investment funds
without identifying them by name. As many as half a dozen
proposals have been received, the newspaper said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
